stage.name: JSON Path With Paths Not In Response
stage.narrative: A test which calls a web api action which is set up with jsonpath output parameters which WILL NOT be returned in the response. The test is checking that the call completes sucessfully when it tries to populate an output parameter of each datatype in the case where the jsonpath does not exist. Additionally it tests one of the cases - that the string output parameter is changed from its initial value to empty (the test could be extended in future by finding a way to perform this check on each of the datatypes).
